        <p data-role="text">The Cen&#xAD;tral Nar&#xAD;cotics Bureau seized a haul of drugs which in&#xAD;cluded 7.55kg of cannabis in an op&#xAD;er&#xAD;a&#xAD;tion last month. Some&#xAD;one&#x2019;s drug ad&#xAD;dic&#xAD;tion can cause much harm to fam&#xAD;i&#xAD;lies and col&#xAD;leagues, says the writer.</p>
    </div>

